Relationships Confirmed by DNA

Terry Crossley and Mary Doyle

Terry Crossley (son of James Joseph Crossley and Joyce Enid Foott) and Mary Doyle are third cousins as documented in the WikiTree database.

Terry Crossley is the great-great grandson of William Greenwood and Margaret (Shanahan) Greenwood:

Terry Crossley is the son of James Joseph Crossley confirmed by DNA

James is the son of John Charles Crossley confirmed by DNA

John is the son of Ann (Greenwood) Crossley confirmed by DNA

Ann is the daughter of William Greenwood and Margaret (Shanahan) Greenwood confirmed by DNA

Mary Doyle is the great-great granddaughter of William Greenwood and Margaret (Shanahan) Greenwood:

Mary Doyle is the daughter of Claud Augustus Doyle confirmed by DNA

Claud Augustus is the son of John Doyle confirmed by DNA

John is the son of Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle confirmed by DNA

Mary Ann is the daughter of William Greenwood and Margaret (Shanahan) Greenwood confirmed by DNA

Paternal and maternal relationships are confirmed by a GEDmatch test match between Terry Crossley GEDmatch A710880 and his third cousin Mary Doyle GEDmatch A333615.

Their most-recent common ancestors (MRCAs) are their great-great grandparents William Greenwood and Margaret (Shanahan) Greenwood.

Estimated number of generations to MRCA = 3.5, based on sharing 111.5 cM across 4 segments (largest segment is 44.9 cM).

Myles Hannan (another third cousin, to both Terry and Mary) categorised the relationships as “Confirmed by DNA”, based on instructions in WikiTree (https://www.wikitree.com/wiki/Help:DNA_Confirmation).

Kim Gabbey and Mary Doyle

Kim (McAuliffe) Gabbey and Mary Doyle are second cousins, once removed as documented in the WikiTree database.

Kim Gabbey is the great-great granddaughter of Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle and Patrick Doyle:

Kim Gabbey is the daughter of John Joseph McAuliffe confirmed by DNA

John is the son of Helen (Baumgardner) McAuliffe confirmed by DNA

Helen is the daughter of Ellen (Doyle) Gardner confirmed by DNA

Ellen is the daughter of Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle and Patrick Doyle confirmed by DNA

Mary Doyle is the great granddaughter of Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle and Patrick Doyle:

Mary Doyle is the daughter of Claud Augustus Doyle confirmed by DNA

Claud Augustus is the son of John Doyle confirmed by DNA

John is the son of Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle and Patrick Doyle confirmed by DNA

As you can see from the paragraphs above, Myles Hannan has categorised various relationships as "confirmed by DNA" because MyHeritage has categorised the DNA match of Kim and Mary as "Parent's 2nd cousin " (Mary) and "2nd cousin's daughter" (Kim):

Names: Mary Doyle & Kim Gabbey, Total (cM): 142.8 (2.0%)

Maternal and paternal relationships are confirmed by a MyHeritageDNA test match between Kim (McAuliffe) Gabbey and Mary Doyle, her 2nd cousin, once removed.

Their most-recent common ancestors are Mary Ann (Greenwood) Doyle and Patrick Doyle, the great-grandparents of Mary Doyle and the great-great-grandparents of Kim (McAuliffe) Gabbey.

Myles Hannan categorised the relationships as “Confirmed by DNA”, based on instructions in WikiTree (https://www.wikitree.com/wiki/Help:DNA_Confirmation).
